import React from "react";
import {Box, Typography, styled, Button, Stack} from "@mui/material"
import Background from "./../Images/HeroBackground.jpg";
import Handy from "./../Images/handy.png";

const RightBox = styled(Box)({
    backgroundImage:`url(${Background})`, 
    backgroundAttachment: "fixed",
    backgroundSize: "80%",
    minHeight:"80vh",
    
});

const Header = styled(Stack)({
    background: "#BFD200",
    textAlign: "left",
});

//StyledBox als Parent von LeftBox und RIghtBox?
export default function Hero() {
    return (
        <Box bgcolor="green">
            <Stack direction="row">
                <Box component="img"
                    src={require("./../Images/handy.png")}
                    flex={1}
                    bgcolor="green">
                </Box>
                <RightBox flex={2}>
                    <Stack direction="column">
                        <Stack direction="row" alignItems="center">
                            <Typography variant="h4">
                                DEIN DIGITALER 
                            </Typography>
                            <Typography variant="h4" sx={{fontWeight:"bold", p:"5px"}}>
                                CO-TRAINER
                            </Typography>
                        </Stack>
                        <Box>

                            <Typography>
                                COACHING MADE EASY
                            </Typography>
                            <Typography>
                                MINIMALER AUFWAND.
                            </Typography>
                            <Typography>
                                MAXIMALER ERFOLG.
                            </Typography>
                            <Typography>
                                Weil der Trainerjob Spa√ü machen soll!
                            </Typography>
                            <Button>
                                LOS GEHT'S
                            </Button>
                        <Stack direction="row">
                            <Stack direction="column">
                                <Typography>
                                    6.000+
                                </Typography>
                                <Typography>
                                    Trainer
                                </Typography>
                            </Stack>
                            <Stack direction="column">
                                <Typography>
                                    5 Mio
                                </Typography>
                                <Typography>
                                    Trainings
                                </Typography>
                            </Stack>
                            <Stack direction="column">
                                <Typography>
                                    3.000+
                                </Typography>
                                <Typography>
                                    Spiele
                                </Typography>
                            </Stack>
                        </Stack>
                        </Box>
                    </Stack>
                </RightBox>
            </Stack>
        </Box>
    )
}
